-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(35,1,'2012-11-07 02:27:27','2012-11-07 02:27:27','If you have the right experience, personality and knowledge, we can help you find your perfect job as a LiveIn Nanny, Live-Out Nanny, Mother\'s Helper, After School care or Nanny-share, permanent or temporary, full time or part time. If you are newly qualified or wish to gain further experience, there are many opportunities to explore, such as being a mother\'s helper or even babysitting.\r\n\r\nIf you have the right qualifications and experience, and you successfully complete a series of checks and the interview process, you will be registered as a Bumble Bees Nannies Childcare Professional.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"divider div2\"></div>\r\n\r\n\"Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies. Being a nanny is a fulfilling and professional career choice, working with children on a one to one level, watching them grow up and develop into little adults. You help them through their stages of development and support them in their everyday choices as they get older. I am here to help you find a great family to work with so you also can enjoy these great experiences like I have. Through my seven years of nanny experience I can offer you extra advice and help when deciding a family/job, from interview advice to finding childcare groups in your neighbourhood. I want to help nannies, and share my knowledge and skills - like others have done for me\"\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>','Caregivers','','publish','open','open','','caregiver','','','2012-12-02 00:46:03','2012-12-02 00:46:03','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=35',0,'page','',0),(36,1,'2012-11-07 02:27:22','2012-11-07 02:27:22','','Nanny','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision','','','2012-11-07 02:27:22','2012-11-07 02:27:22','',35,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/35-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(37,1,'2012-11-07 02:28:10','2012-11-07 02:28:10',' ','','','publish','open','open',