nnying comes very naturally and quickly to these teachers, they have the extra knowledge that is so important in the first 5 years of a child’s life.\r\n\r\nMany students completing their Bachelor in Education or Diploma in Early Childhood from recognized Colleges are looking to be nannies. They enjoy being nanny’s more because it involves one on one education and care. They get to educate and care for children to the best of their knowledge, to see your children grow and develop and to teach them.\r\n\r\nHaving a newly qualified teacher in your home is fantastic, they understand so much about children and specialize in Early Childhood development.\r\n\r\nEC students study Human Development theorists - Vygotsky, Piaget and Freund - who have spent many years researching how children learn.\r\n\r\nEarly Childhood students know\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ages and Stages in human development</li>\r\n	<li>Socialization skills</li>\r\n	<li>The different types of play</li>\r\n	<li>Age appropriate play.</li>\r\n	<li>Physical development (gross and fine motor).</li>\r\n	<li>Cognitive development</li>\r\n	<li>Emotional stages that children go through</li>\r\n	<li>They have a natural ability to observe children and ask questions</li>\r\n	<li>Understand to ask open ended questions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEarly Childhood teachers have that special touch. During their education they are placed in different settings such as day cares and primary schools and are there for around 3 months at a time. During this stage they practice their knowledge that they have learnt in the classroom and are watched and critiqued by their lectures.\r\n\r\nIn a Nanny and Nanny Share setting Early Childhood educators are affordable.','Early Childhood Educator As Your Nanny','','publish','open','open','','early-childhood-educator-as-your-nanny','','','2012-12-02 01:26:52','2012-12-02 01:26:52','',154,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=300',0,'page','',0),(301,1,'2012-12-02 01:26:08','2012-12-02 01:26:08','Bumble Bee